        "text": "(ax+4)(3x 2 −bx+5)=18x 3 −6x 2 +18x+20 ⁣‍‌‍‌‌‌‍‍‌‌‍‍‌‍‍‍‍‍‍‌‌‍‌‍‍‍‍‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‍‌‍‍‍‌‍‌‍‍⁤ The equation above is true for all values of  x, ⁣‍‌‍‌‌‌‍‍‌‌‍‍‌‍‍‍‍‍‍‌‌‍‌‍‍‍‍‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‍‌‍‍‍‌‍‌‍‍⁤where  a and  b are constants. What is the value of ab? A):12 B): 24 C):6 D):18"
      },
      {
